data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Murrieta! This immaculate single-story gem is a rare find with NO HOA, RV parking, and exquisite upgrades that will take your breath away. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the open-concept design and the attention to detail that has been poured into every corner of this home. As you enter, custom plantation shutters and ship lap accents welcome you into the spacious living area. The coffered ceilings and wainscotting on the walls adds a touch of elegance, setting the tone for the entire home. Board and batten paneling graces the walls, adding a modern yet timeless charm that flows seamlessly throughout. The kitchen is a true masterpiece, boasting stainless steel appliances and a full backsplash that reaches to the ceiling. Cooking enthusiasts will appreciate the convenience of a pot filler and a custom range hood. Soft-close drawers and luxurious LVP flooring make this kitchen as functional as it is beautiful. The family room is the perfect gathering spot, featuring a cozy fireplace with a custom hearth, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Window casing throughout adds a touch of sophistication to the living spaces. The bedrooms offer built-in closets for ample storage, and the bathrooms are nothing short of spectacular. Each bathroom is custom-designed with marble showers, quartz countertops, and wainscotting, creating a spa-like experience right at home. Step outside to your private oasis – the backyard is spacious enough for a future pool and features an oversized alumawood patio cover, ideal for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Exterior of home was recently painted. Conveniently located close to shopping and easy freeway access, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this upgraded single-story residence in Murrieta your forever home. Don't wait as this home will not last long!
